    <section id="our-project" class="centered-content">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Be the change you want to see</h1>
            <p>Climate change and environmental issues are affecting all of us. In the face of the huge global crisis we see in the media, many people feel powerless to act and make a difference. Planet Friendly Schools show how we can all make small changes in our lifestyles and inspire people to be the change they want to see. We want to empower schools, together with the communities they serve, to make change happen!</p>
            <a class="btn btn-dark" href="/about-the-project">About us</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="inspiration" class="centered-content">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Get inspired</h1>
            <p>Why not start your journey to becoming a Planet Friendly School? Get inspired to work on projects in your school, reach out to your community and join a movement of schools across Europe that are looking after our planet.</p>

